data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bed, 1.5 bath Two-Story home in the Town of Poughkeepsie, Hyde Park Schools! Situated on a private dead end street on a nice level lot, this property has a spacious front yard perfect for outdoor enjoyment and entertaining! Home features ample living space ideal for comfortable living and entertaining. First floor boasts a lower level bedroom, family room, dining area, living room and powder room. Upstairs you will find a spacious primary, well sized second bedroom or excellent office space and a full bathroom. Amazing location, close to schools, shops, excellent restaurants, downtown Poughkeepsie, the Walkway Over the Hudson, Marist College and Culinary Institute. Municipal water and sewer! Don't miss the opportunity, PRICED TO SELL!
